{"tid":2198589,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"證監會暗示警邊無按合作機制要求合作調查壹傳媒案件","createTime":"2020-09-11T12:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T12:40:54.000Z","uid":271894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b039008465be12aec3d04bbc3d1e2e04ea77eff3","tid":2198589,"uid":271894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:37:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/urgentnews.jsp?taskId=18496&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Furgentnews.jsp%3FtaskId%3D18496%26refer%3DShare&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fvcbRDcn212Q0H9cnoVtDxk%3D&h=b3daccfa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Furgentnews.jsp%3FtaskId%3D18496%26refer%3DShare&h=96d704c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/urgentnews.jsp?taskId=18496&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】證監會就警方調查壹傳媒股份涉及虛假交易罕有發聲明回應，暗示警方並無按照雙方既有的合作機制提出協助要求。 <br />\n<br />\n證監會的聲明引述警務處與證監會簽訂的備忘錄，指雙方承諾就證券市場的罪案盡量互相協調和合作，聲明沒有提及警方是否有就案件要求協助，但就指證監會已經準備好回應警務處按備忘錄而提出的任何協助要求。<br />\n<br />\n證監會的聲明又指，虛假交易是屬於證券及期貨條例下的罪行，而對於違反證券條例的行為，證監會有責任去調查和執法，故此基於公眾利益，有需要就事件釐清本身的立場。<br />\n<br />\n姐係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n證監會覺得無問題 但係狗有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842f2afd84ce14ed56dbd940fce10a89a884e92f","tid":2198589,"uid":271894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:39:52.000Z","msg":"自己推下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p